body_html: I am probably not going to merge this. It turns out that even if we enforce valid identifiers, we still end up with arbitrary other restrictions in serialization (no python keywords, for instance) and have to do further renaming there. So it seems like we don't actually need this, and would complicate the API since ONNX would still need a separate path.
